Roach Says Advanced Economies on Cusp of Synchronized Recession

-- B y   S c o t t   H a m i l t o n
-- 
2011-09-22T12:12:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/roach-says-advanced-economies-on-cusp-of-synchronized-recession.html
Stephen Roach , non-executive
chairman of Morgan Stanley  Asia , said the world’s “advanced
economies are on the brink of a synchronised recession.”  Roach made the comments in an interview on CNBC today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
